name: This is a sample event on how to fill up this file. For whitelistEvents.json: all fields are required. For blacklistEvents.json: id, formatted_time and url are required. Time fields are filled in as an example for time format DD MMM YYYY, ddd, h:mm a.
PyLadies SG July 2015 Meetup - Introduction to Python
description: Martin Brochhaus, one of PyCon SG's organizers, will join us and give a little presentation about how to install Python on Windows, OSX or Ubuntu. He will also show how to use the free editor Atom.io as a Python IDE and guide us through the first steps of writing a Python program.
location: PayPal office at 5 Temasek Boulevard, Level 7, Suntec Tower 5, Singapore 038985
